{
  "video_id": "VqtEppZmjfw",
  "title": "William Noel: Revealing the lost codex of Archimedes",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15731.0,
      "end_time": 18215.0,
      "text": "The great texts of the ancient world"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18215.0,
      "end_time": 21530.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t survive to us in their original form."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21530.0,
      "end_time": 25490.0,
      "text": "They survive because medieval scribes copied them"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25490.0,
      "end_time": 27480.0,
      "text": "and copied them and copied them."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27480.0,
      "end_time": 29697.0,
      "text": "And so it is with Archimedes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29698.0,
      "end_time": 31464.0,
      "text": "the great Greek mathematician."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31464.0,
      "end_time": 34466.0,
      "text": "Everything we know about Archimedes as a mathematician"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34466.0,
      "end_time": 37164.0,
      "text": "we know about because of just three books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37164.0,
      "end_time": 39800.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re called A, B and C."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39800.0,
      "end_time": 43913.0,
      "text": "And A was lost by an Italian humanist in 1564."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43913.0,
      "end_time": 46715.0,
      "text": "And B was last heard of in the Pope&#39;s Library"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46716.0,
      "end_time": 52548.0,
      "text": "about a hundred miles north of Rome in Viterbo in 1311."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52548.0,
      "end_time": 56845.0,
      "text": "Now Codex C was only discovered in 1906,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56845.0,
      "end_time": 59394.0,
      "text": "and it landed on my desk in Baltimore"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59394.0,
      "end_time": 63519.0,
      "text": "on the 19th of January, 1999."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63520.0,
      "end_time": 65938.0,
      "text": "And this is Codex C here."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65938.0,
      "end_time": 71107.0,
      "text": "Now Codex C is actually buried in this book."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71107.0,
      "end_time": 72557.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s buried treasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72557.0,
      "end_time": 74892.0,
      "text": "Because this book is actually a prayer book."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74892.0,
      "end_time": 77856.0,
      "text": "It was finished by a guy called Johannes Myrones"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77856.0,
      "end_time": 81473.0,
      "text": "on the 14th of April, 1229."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81473.0,
      "end_time": 83958.0,
      "text": "And to make his prayer book he used parchment."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83958.0,
      "end_time": 86373.0,
      "text": "But he didn&#39;t use new parchment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86373.0,
      "end_time": 89687.0,
      "text": "he used parchment recycled from earlier manuscripts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89687.0,
      "end_time": 91423.0,
      "text": "and there were seven of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91424.0,
      "end_time": 94907.0,
      "text": "And Archimedes Codex C was just one of those seven."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94907.0,
      "end_time": 100374.0,
      "text": "He took apart the Archimedes manuscript and the other seven manuscripts."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100374.0,
      "end_time": 103756.0,
      "text": "He erased all of their texts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103757.0,
      "end_time": 106175.0,
      "text": "and then he cut the sheets down in the middle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106175.0,
      "end_time": 108419.0,
      "text": "he shuffled them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108419.0,
      "end_time": 110337.0,
      "text": "and he rotated them 90 degrees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110337.0,
      "end_time": 112389.0,
      "text": "and he wrote prayers on top of these books."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112389.0,
      "end_time": 114860.0,
      "text": "And essentially these seven manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114860.0,
      "end_time": 118434.0,
      "text": "disappeared for 700 years, and we have a prayer book."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118434.0,
      "end_time": 121683.0,
      "text": "The prayer book was discovered by this guy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121683.0,
      "end_time": 124410.0,
      "text": "Johan Ludvig Heiberg, in 1906."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124410.0,
      "end_time": 125851.0,
      "text": "And with just a magnifying glass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125851.0,
      "end_time": 128734.0,
      "text": "he transcribed as much of the text as he could."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128735.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131917.0,
      "text": "And the thing is that he found two texts in this manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131917.0,
      "end_time": 133685.0,
      "text": "that were unique texts."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133685.0,
      "end_time": 135285.0,
      "text": "They weren&#39;t in A and B at all;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135285.0,
      "end_time": 136983.0,
      "text": "they were completely new texts by Archimedes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136983.0,
      "end_time": 140218.0,
      "text": "and they were called \"The Method\" and \"The Stomachion.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140218.0,
      "end_time": 142487.0,
      "text": "And it became a world famous manuscript."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142487.0,
      "end_time": 144302.0,
      "text": "Now it should be clear by now"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144302.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "that this book is in bad condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147160.0,
      "end_time": 150486.0,
      "text": "It got in worse condition in the 20th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150486.0,
      "end_time": 152218.0,
      "text": "after Heiberg saw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152218.0,
      "end_time": 153734.0,
      "text": "Forgeries were painted over it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153735.0,
      "end_time": 156818.0,
      "text": "and it suffered very badly from mold."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156818.0,
      "end_time": 160568.0,
      "text": "This book is the definition of a write-off."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160568.0,
      "end_time": 162302.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the sort of book"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 162302.0,
      "end_time": 164966.0,
      "text": "that you thought would be in an institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 164967.0,
      "end_time": 167153.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not in an institution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167153.0,
      "end_time": 171785.0,
      "text": "it was bought by a private owner in 1998."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171785.0,
      "end_time": 173535.0,
      "text": "Why did he buy this book?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173535.0,
      "end_time": 177720.0,
      "text": "Because he wanted to make that which was fragile safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177720.0,
      "end_time": 180318.0,
      "text": "He wanted to make that which was unique ubiquitous."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 180318.0,
      "end_time": 184984.0,
      "text": "He wanted to make that which was expensive free."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184984.0,
      "end_time": 188119.0,
      "text": "And he wanted to do this as a matter of principle."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188119.0,
      "end_time": 192651.0,
      "text": "Because not many people are really going to read Archimedes in ancient Greek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192651.0,
      "end_time": 195335.0,
      "text": "but they should have the chance to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 195335.0,
      "end_time": 198634.0,
      "text": "So he gathered around himself the friends of Archimedes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 198634.0,
      "end_time": 200769.0,
      "text": "and he promised to pay for all the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200770.0,
      "end_time": 202468.0,
      "text": "And it was an expensive job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202468.0,
      "end_time": 205938.0,
      "text": "but actually it wouldn&#39;t be as much as you think"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 205938.0,
      "end_time": 208102.0,
      "text": "because these people, they didn&#39;t come from money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 208103.0,
      "end_time": 209922.0,
      "text": "they came from Archimedes."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209922.0,
      "end_time": 211638.0,
      "text": "And they came from all sorts of different backgrounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211638.0,
      "end_time": 213821.0,
      "text": "They came from particle physics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213821.0,
      "end_time": 215387.0,
      "text": "they came from classical philology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215387.0,
      "end_time": 217355.0,
      "text": "they came from book conservation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217355.0,
      "end_time": 219936.0,
      "text": "they came from ancient mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 219937.0,
      "end_time": 221854.0,
      "text": "they came from data management,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221854.0,
      "end_time": 224771.0,
      "text": "they came from scientific imaging and program management."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224771.0,
      "end_time": 228327.0,
      "text": "And they got together to work on this manuscript."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228327.0,
      "end_time": 232138.0,
      "text": "The first problem was a conservation problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232138.0,
      "end_time": 234571.0,
      "text": "And this is the sort of thing that we had to deal with:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 234571.0,
      "end_time": 236771.0,
      "text": "There was glue on the spine of the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 236771.0,
      "end_time": 238971.0,
      "text": "And if you look at this photograph carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238972.0,
      "end_time": 241200.0,
      "text": "the bottom half of this is rather brown."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241200.0,
      "end_time": 242388.0,
      "text": "And that glue is hide glue."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 242388.0,
      "end_time": 243773.0,
      "text": "Now if you&#39;re a conservator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243773.0,
      "end_time": 245905.0,
      "text": "you can take off this glue reasonably easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 245905.0,
      "end_time": 249270.0,
      "text": "The top half is Elmer&#39;s wood glue."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 249270.0,
      "end_time": 251387.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s polyvinyl acetate emulsion"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 251387.0,
      "end_time": 254540.0,
      "text": "that doesn&#39;t dissolve in water once it&#39;s dry."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 254540.0,
      "end_time": 257220.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s much tougher than the parchment that it was written on."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 257220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260571.00000000003,
      "text": "And so before we could start imaging Archimedes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 260571.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262200.0,
      "text": "we had to take this book apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262190.0,
      "end_time": 264871.0,
      "text": "So it took four years to take apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264871.0,
      "end_time": 268404.0,
      "text": "And this is a rare action shot, ladies and gentlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268404.0,
      "end_time": 271175.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271175.0,
      "end_time": 275441.0,
      "text": "Another thing is that we had to get rid of all the wax,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275441.0,
      "end_time": 277676.0,
      "text": "because this was used in the liturgical services"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 277676.0,
      "end_time": 279417.0,
      "text": "of the Greek Orthodox Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 279417.0,
      "end_time": 280727.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d used candle wax."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280728.0,
      "end_time": 282591.0,
      "text": "And the candle wax was dirty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 282591.0,
      "end_time": 283824.0,
      "text": "and we couldn&#39;t image through the wax."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 283824.0,
      "end_time": 287159.0,
      "text": "So very carefully we had to mechanically scrape off all the wax."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 287159.0,
      "end_time": 289610.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to tell you exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 289610.0,
      "end_time": 291775.0,
      "text": "how bad this condition of this book is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 291775.0,
      "end_time": 294541.0,
      "text": "but it came out in little bits very often."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 294541.0,
      "end_time": 296891.0,
      "text": "And normally in a book, you wouldn&#39;t worry about the little bits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 296891.0,
      "end_time": 299891.0,
      "text": "but these little bits might contain unique Archimedes text."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 299891.0,
      "end_time": 302190.0,
      "text": "So, tiny fragments"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 302190.0,
      "end_time": 306931.0,
      "text": "we actually managed to put back in the right place."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 306931.0,
      "end_time": 310640.0,
      "text": "Then, having done that, we started to image the manuscript."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 310641.0,
      "end_time": 312141.0,
      "text": "And we imaged the manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 312141.0,
      "end_time": 314169.0,
      "text": "in 14 different wavebands of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 314169.0,
      "end_time": 318750.0,
      "text": "Because if you look at something in different wavebands of light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318750.0,
      "end_time": 319291.0,
      "text": "you see different things."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319291.0,
      "end_time": 320858.0,
      "text": "And here is an image of a page"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 320858.0,
      "end_time": 323375.0,
      "text": "imaged in 14 different wavebands of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 323375.0,
      "end_time": 325508.0,
      "text": "But none of them worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 325508.0,
      "end_time": 329924.0,
      "text": "So what we did was we processed the images together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 329925.0,
      "end_time": 333225.0,
      "text": "and we put two images into one blank screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 333225.0,
      "end_time": 336580.0,
      "text": "And here are two different images of the Archimedes manuscript."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 336580.0,
      "end_time": 337873.0,
      "text": "And the image on the left"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 337874.0,
      "end_time": 339225.0,
      "text": "is the normal red image."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 339225.0,
      "end_time": 341137.0,
      "text": "And the image on the right is an ultraviolet image."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 341137.0,
      "end_time": 342277.0,
      "text": "And in the image on the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 342277.0,
      "end_time": 344724.0,
      "text": "you might be able to see some of the Archimedes writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 344725.0,
      "end_time": 347707.0,
      "text": "If you merge them together into one digital canvas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 347707.0,
      "end_time": 350525.0,
      "text": "the parchment is bright in both images"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 350525.0,
      "end_time": 352400.0,
      "text": "and it comes out bright."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 352400.0,
      "end_time": 355416.0,
      "text": "The prayer book is dark in both images"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 355416.0,
      "end_time": 357113.0,
      "text": "and it comes out dark."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 357113.0,
      "end_time": 360464.0,
      "text": "The Archimedes text is dark in one image and bright in another."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 360464.0,
      "end_time": 362864.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;ll come out dark but red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 362864.0,
      "end_time": 365131.0,
      "text": "and then you can start to read it rather clearly."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 365131.0,
      "end_time": 367972.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what it looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 367973.0,
      "end_time": 371315.0,
      "text": "Now that&#39;s a before and after image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 371315.0,
      "end_time": 374297.0,
      "text": "but you don&#39;t read the image on the screen like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 374297.0,
      "end_time": 376916.0,
      "text": "You zoom in and you zoom in"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376916.0,
      "end_time": 380464.0,
      "text": "and you zoom in and you zoom in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 380464.0,
      "end_time": 382532.0,
      "text": "and you can just read it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 382532.0,
      "end_time": 388880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 388880.0,
      "end_time": 392460.0,
      "text": "If you process the same two images in a different way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 392460.0,
      "end_time": 395300.0,
      "text": "you can actually get rid of the prayer book text."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 395300.0,
      "end_time": 396470.0,
      "text": "And this is terribly important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 396480.0,
      "end_time": 399310.0,
      "text": "because the diagrams in the manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 399310.0,
      "end_time": 401498.0,
      "text": "are the unique source for the diagrams"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 401498.0,
      "end_time": 404315.0,
      "text": "that Archimedes drew in the sand in the fourth century B.C."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 404315.0,
      "end_time": 407354.0,
      "text": "And there we are, I can give them to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 407354.0,
      "end_time": 409698.0,
      "text": "With this kind of imaging --"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 409698.0,
      "end_time": 412364.0,
      "text": "this kind of infrared, ultraviolet, invisible light imaging --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 412364.0,
      "end_time": 414964.0,
      "text": "we were never going to image through the gold ground forgeries."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 414964.0,
      "end_time": 416817.0,
      "text": "How were we going to do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 416817.0,
      "end_time": 418780.0,
      "text": "Well we took the manuscript,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418780.0,
      "end_time": 423660.0,
      "text": "and we decided to image it in X-ray fluorescence imaging."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 423670.0,
      "end_time": 426810.0,
      "text": "So an X-ray comes in in the diagram on the left"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 426810.0,
      "end_time": 429933.0,
      "text": "and it knocks out an electron from the inner shell of an atom."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 429933.0,
      "end_time": 431931.0,
      "text": "And that electron disappears."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 431931.0,
      "end_time": 435566.0,
      "text": "And as it disappears, an electron from a shell farther out"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 435566.0,
      "end_time": 438480.0,
      "text": "jumps in and takes its place."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 438480.0,
      "end_time": 439481.0,
      "text": "And when it takes its place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 439481.0,
      "end_time": 442315.0,
      "text": "it sheds electromagnetic radiation."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 442315.0,
      "end_time": 443747.0,
      "text": "It sheds an X-ray."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 443747.0,
      "end_time": 446398.0,
      "text": "And this X-ray is specific in its wavelength"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 446398.0,
      "end_time": 448280.0,
      "text": "to the atom that it hits."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 448280.0,
      "end_time": 450448.0,
      "text": "And what we wanted to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 450448.0,
      "end_time": 452181.0,
      "text": "was the iron."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 452181.0,
      "end_time": 454480.0,
      "text": "Because the ink was written in iron."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 454480.0,
      "end_time": 455731.0,
      "text": "And if we can map"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 455731.0,
      "end_time": 458315.0,
      "text": "where this X-ray that comes out, where it comes from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 458315.0,
      "end_time": 460381.0,
      "text": "we can map all the iron on the page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 460381.0,
      "end_time": 462979.0,
      "text": "then theoretically we can read the image."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 462980.0,
      "end_time": 467315.0,
      "text": "The thing is that you need a very powerful light source to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 467315.0,
      "end_time": 470689.0,
      "text": "So we took it to the Stanford Synchrotron Radiation Laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 470689.0,
      "end_time": 472131.0,
      "text": "in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 472131.0,
      "end_time": 473698.0,
      "text": "which is a particle accelerator."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 473699.0,
      "end_time": 475431.0,
      "text": "Electrons go around one way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 475431.0,
      "end_time": 477480.0,
      "text": "positrons go around the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 477480.0,
      "end_time": 478364.0,
      "text": "They meet in the middle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 478364.0,
      "end_time": 480799.0,
      "text": "and they create subatomic particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 480800.0,
      "end_time": 483300.0,
      "text": "like the charm quark and the tau lepton."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 483300.0,
      "end_time": 486510.0,
      "text": "Now we weren&#39;t actually going to put Archimedes in that beam."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 486520.0,
      "end_time": 489600.0,
      "text": "But as the electrons go round at the speed of light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 489600.0,
      "end_time": 490867.0,
      "text": "they shed X-rays."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 490867.0,
      "end_time": 493517.0,
      "text": "And this is the most powerful light source in the solar system."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 493517.0,
      "end_time": 495466.0,
      "text": "This is called synchrotron radiation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 495466.0,
      "end_time": 497284.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s normally used to look at things"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 497284.0,
      "end_time": 498950.0,
      "text": "like proteins and that sort of thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 498951.0,
      "end_time": 502948.0,
      "text": "But we wanted it to look at atoms, at iron atoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 502948.0,
      "end_time": 505817.0,
      "text": "so that we could read the page from before and after."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 505817.0,
      "end_time": 508115.0,
      "text": "And lo and behold, we found that we could do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 508115.0,
      "end_time": 511563.0,
      "text": "It took about 17 minutes to do a single page."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 511563.0,
      "end_time": 514217.0,
      "text": "So what did we discover?"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 514217.0,
      "end_time": 516400.0,
      "text": "Well one of the unique texts in Archimedes"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 516400.0,
      "end_time": 518203.0,
      "text": "is called \"The Stomachion.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 518203.0,
      "end_time": 520616.0,
      "text": "And this didn&#39;t exist in Codices A and B."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 520616.0,
      "end_time": 523350.0,
      "text": "And we knew that it involved this square."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 523350.0,
      "end_time": 524829.0,
      "text": "And this is a perfect square,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 524829.0,
      "end_time": 526849.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s divided into 14 bits."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 526850.0,
      "end_time": 529633.0,
      "text": "But no one knew what Archimedes was doing with these 14 bits."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 529633.0,
      "end_time": 531817.0,
      "text": "And now we think we know."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 531817.0,
      "end_time": 533584.0,
      "text": "He was trying to work out"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 533584.0,
      "end_time": 536117.0,
      "text": "how many ways you can recombine those 14 bits"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 536117.0,
      "end_time": 538444.0,
      "text": "and still make a perfect square."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 538444.0,
      "end_time": 541945.0,
      "text": "Anyone want to guess the answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 541946.0,
      "end_time": 547308.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 17,152 divided into 536 families."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 547308.0,
      "end_time": 549675.0,
      "text": "And the important point about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 549675.0,
      "end_time": 553389.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s the earliest study in combinatorics in mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 553389.0,
      "end_time": 557153.0,
      "text": "And combinatorics is a wonderful and interesting branch of mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 557153.0,
      "end_time": 560388.0,
      "text": "The really astonishing thing though about this manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 560388.0,
      "end_time": 562757.0,
      "text": "is that we looked at the other manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 562757.0,
      "end_time": 564175.0,
      "text": "that the palimpsester had made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 564175.0,
      "end_time": 566741.0,
      "text": "the scribe had made his book out of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 566741.0,
      "end_time": 569673.0,
      "text": "and one of them was a manuscript containing text by Hyperides."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 569673.0,
      "end_time": 574410.0,
      "text": "Now Hyperides was an Athenian orator from the fourth century B.C."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 574410.0,
      "end_time": 576458.0,
      "text": "He was an exact contemporary of Demosthenes."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 576458.0,
      "end_time": 580857.0,
      "text": "And in 338 B.C. he and Demosthenes together"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 580857.0,
      "end_time": 582540.0,
      "text": "decided that they wanted to stand up"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 582541.0,
      "end_time": 584541.0,
      "text": "to the military might of Philip of Macedon."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 584541.0,
      "end_time": 588190.0,
      "text": "So Athens and Thebes went out to fight Philip of Macedon."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 588190.0,
      "end_time": 589458.0,
      "text": "This was a bad idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 589458.0,
      "end_time": 592891.0,
      "text": "because Philip of Macedon had a son called Alexander the Great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 592891.0,
      "end_time": 595174.0,
      "text": "and they lost the battle of Chaeronea."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 595174.0,
      "end_time": 597891.0,
      "text": "Alexander the Great went on to conquer the known world;"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 597892.0,
      "end_time": 600642.0,
      "text": "Hyperides found himself on trial for treason."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 600642.0,
      "end_time": 604242.0,
      "text": "And this is the speech that he gave when he was on trial --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 604242.0,
      "end_time": 605390.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a great speech:"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 605390.0,
      "end_time": 607658.0,
      "text": "\"Best of all,\" he says, \"is to win."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 607658.0,
      "end_time": 609392.0,
      "text": "But if you can&#39;t win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 609392.0,
      "end_time": 611433.0,
      "text": "then you should fight for a noble cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 611433.0,
      "end_time": 613800.0,
      "text": "because then you&#39;ll be remembered."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 613800.0,
      "end_time": 614606.0,
      "text": "Consider the Spartans."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 614606.0,
      "end_time": 616474.0,
      "text": "They won enumerable victories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 616474.0,
      "end_time": 618306.0,
      "text": "but no one remembers what they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 618306.0,
      "end_time": 620441.0,
      "text": "because they were all fought for selfish ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 620441.0,
      "end_time": 624700.0,
      "text": "The one battle that the Spartans fought that everybody remembers"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 624700.0,
      "end_time": 625723.0,
      "text": "is the the battle of Thermopylae"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 625723.0,
      "end_time": 627726.0,
      "text": "where they were butchered to a man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 627726.0,
      "end_time": 629658.0,
      "text": "but fought for the freedom of Greece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 629658.0,
      "end_time": 631923.0,
      "text": "It was such a great speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 631923.0,
      "end_time": 635658.0,
      "text": "that the Athenian law courts let him off."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 635658.0,
      "end_time": 637724.0,
      "text": "He lived for another 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 637724.0,
      "end_time": 640375.0,
      "text": "then the Macedonian faction caught up with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 640375.0,
      "end_time": 642959.0,
      "text": "They cut out his tongue in mockery of his oratory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 642959.0,
      "end_time": 646390.0,
      "text": "and no one knows what they did with his body."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 646390.0,
      "end_time": 649540.0,
      "text": "So this is the discovery of a lost voice from antiquity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 649541.0,
      "end_time": 651523.0,
      "text": "speaking to us, not from the grave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 651523.0,
      "end_time": 653100.0,
      "text": "because his grave doesn&#39;t exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 653100.0,
      "end_time": 654774.0,
      "text": "but from the Athenian law courts."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 654774.0,
      "end_time": 656423.0,
      "text": "Now I should say at this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 656423.0,
      "end_time": 659190.0,
      "text": "that normally when you&#39;re looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 659190.0,
      "end_time": 661186.0,
      "text": "at medieval manuscripts that have been scraped off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 661186.0,
      "end_time": 662672.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t find unique texts."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 662672.0,
      "end_time": 665774.0,
      "text": "And to find two in one manuscript is really something."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 665774.0,
      "end_time": 668991.0,
      "text": "To find three is completely weird."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 668991.0,
      "end_time": 670672.0,
      "text": "And we found three."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 670672.0,
      "end_time": 671938.0,
      "text": "Aristotle&#39;s \"Categories\""
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 671938.0,
      "end_time": 674391.0,
      "text": "is one of the foundational texts of Western philosophy."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 674391.0,
      "end_time": 678807.0,
      "text": "And we found a third century A.D. commentary on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 678807.0,
      "end_time": 681991.0,
      "text": "possibly by Galen and probably by Porphyry."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 681991.0,
      "end_time": 684189.0,
      "text": "Now all this data that we collected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 684189.0,
      "end_time": 686723.0,
      "text": "all the images, all the raw images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 686724.0,
      "end_time": 689740.0,
      "text": "all the transcriptions that we made and that sort of thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 689740.0,
      "end_time": 692560.0,
      "text": "have been put online under a Creative Commons license"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 692560.0,
      "end_time": 695473.0,
      "text": "for anyone to use for any commercial purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 695474.0,
      "end_time": 702700.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 702700.0,
      "end_time": 705310.0,
      "text": "Why did the owner of the manuscript do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 705311.0,
      "end_time": 709570.0,
      "text": "He did this because he understands data as well as books."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 709570.0,
      "end_time": 710392.0,
      "text": "Now the thing to do with books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 710392.0,
      "end_time": 712523.0,
      "text": "if you want to ensure their long-term utility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 712523.0,
      "end_time": 714739.0,
      "text": "is to hide them away in closets"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 714739.0,
      "end_time": 716539.0,
      "text": "and let very few people look at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 716539.0,
      "end_time": 718958.0,
      "text": "The thing to do with data, if you want it to survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 718958.0,
      "end_time": 722259.0,
      "text": "is to let it out and have everybody have it"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 722259.0,
      "end_time": 725358.0,
      "text": "with as little control on that data as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 725358.0,
      "end_time": 726521.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 726522.0,
      "end_time": 729950.0,
      "text": "And institutions can learn from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 729950.0,
      "end_time": 732502.0,
      "text": "Because institutions at the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 732502.0,
      "end_time": 735559.0,
      "text": "confine their data with copyright restrictions and that sort of thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 735559.0,
      "end_time": 737751.0,
      "text": "And if you want to look at medieval manuscripts on the Web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 737751.0,
      "end_time": 741222.0,
      "text": "at the moment you have to go to the National Library of Y&#39;s site"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 741222.0,
      "end_time": 743890.0,
      "text": "or the University Library of X&#39;s site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 743890.0,
      "end_time": 745789.0,
      "text": "which is about the most boring way"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 745789.0,
      "end_time": 747566.0,
      "text": "in which you can deal with digital data."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 747566.0,
      "end_time": 750559.0,
      "text": "What you want to do is to aggregate it all together."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 750559.0,
      "end_time": 753656.0,
      "text": "Because the Web of the ancient manuscripts of the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 753656.0,
      "end_time": 755941.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t going to be built by institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 755942.0,
      "end_time": 759500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to be built by users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 759500.0,
      "end_time": 760824.0,
      "text": "by people who get this data together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 760824.0,
      "end_time": 764358.0,
      "text": "by people who want to aggregate all sorts of maps"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 764359.0,
      "end_time": 765991.0,
      "text": "from wherever they come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 765991.0,
      "end_time": 767790.0,
      "text": "all sorts of medieval romances"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 767791.0,
      "end_time": 769340.0,
      "text": "from wherever they come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 769340.0,
      "end_time": 773123.0,
      "text": "people who just want to curate their own glorious selection"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 773123.0,
      "end_time": 774640.0,
      "text": "of beautiful things."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 774640.0,
      "end_time": 776257.0,
      "text": "And that is the future of the Web."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 776257.0,
      "end_time": 779439.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s an attractive and beautiful future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 779440.0,
      "end_time": 781420.0,
      "text": "if only we can make it happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 781420.0,
      "end_time": 784223.0,
      "text": "Now we at the Walters Art Museum have followed this example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 784223.0,
      "end_time": 787573.0,
      "text": "and we have put up all our manuscripts on the Web"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 787573.0,
      "end_time": 789256.0,
      "text": "for people to enjoy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 789256.0,
      "end_time": 791839.0,
      "text": "all the raw data, all the descriptions, all the metadata."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 791840.0,
      "end_time": 794723.0,
      "text": "under a Creative Commons license."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 794723.0,
      "end_time": 796241.0,
      "text": "Now the Walters Art Museum is a small museum"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 796241.0,
      "end_time": 797789.0,
      "text": "and it has beautiful manuscripts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 797789.0,
      "end_time": 799807.0,
      "text": "but the data is fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 799807.0,
      "end_time": 801590.0,
      "text": "And the result of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 801590.0,
      "end_time": 804608.0,
      "text": "is that if you do a Google search on images right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 804608.0,
      "end_time": 807939.0,
      "text": "and you type in \"Illuminated manuscript Koran\" for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 807940.0,
      "end_time": 812357.0,
      "text": "24 of the 28 images you&#39;ll find come from my institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 812357.0,
      "end_time": 817906.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 817907.0,
      "end_time": 822940.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s think about this for a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 822940.0,
      "end_time": 824923.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s in it for the institution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 824923.0,
      "end_time": 827519.0,
      "text": "There are all sorts of things that are in it for the institution."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 827519.0,
      "end_time": 829642.0,
      "text": "You can talk about the Humanities and that sort of thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 829642.0,
      "end_time": 831523.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s talk about selfish things."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 831523.0,
      "end_time": 835391.0,
      "text": "Because what&#39;s really in it for the institution is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 835391.0,
      "end_time": 838447.0,
      "text": "Now why do people go to the Louvre?"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 838447.0,
      "end_time": 841431.0,
      "text": "They go to see the Mona Lisa."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 841431.0,
      "end_time": 844490.0,
      "text": "Why do they go to see the Mona Lisa?"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 844490.0,
      "end_time": 846872.0,
      "text": "Because they already know what she looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 846872.0,
      "end_time": 849205.0,
      "text": "And they know what she looks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 849206.0,
      "end_time": 853908.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;ve seen pictures of her absolutely everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 853908.0,
      "end_time": 858357.0,
      "text": "Now, there is no need"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 858357.0,
      "end_time": 860636.0,
      "text": "for these restrictions at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 860636.0,
      "end_time": 862723.0,
      "text": "And I think that institutions should stand up"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 862723.0,
      "end_time": 865857.0,
      "text": "and release all their data under unrestricted licenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 865857.0,
      "end_time": 868730.0,
      "text": "and it would be a great benefit to everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 868730.0,
      "end_time": 871239.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t we just let everybody have access to this data"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 871239.0,
      "end_time": 873575.0,
      "text": "and curate their own collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 873575.0,
      "end_time": 875740.0,
      "text": "of ancient knowledge and wonderful and beautiful things"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 875740.0,
      "end_time": 878828.0,
      "text": "and increase the beauty and the cultural significance"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 878828.0,
      "end_time": 880550.0,
      "text": "of the Internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 880560.0,
      "end_time": 881573.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much indeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 881573.0,
      "end_time": 886600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}